---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadForm from '../../components/LeadForm.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Costa Blanca Property for Sale | Apartments & Villas Spain"
  description="Buy property on the Costa Blanca — Alicante, Torrevieja, Benidorm and beyond. Affordable apartments and villas on Spain's White Coast."
  canonical="https://realestateincostadelsol.com/costa-blanca/"
  ogImage="/og/costa-blanca.jpg"
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-animate style="--anim-delay:100ms">Costa Blanca</span>
      <h1 data-animate style="--anim-delay:220ms">Costa Blanca Property for Sale</h1>
      <p data-animate style="--anim-delay:340ms">Spain's White Coast — 200km of Mediterranean coastline with some of the most affordable property prices in the country.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="area-content">
    <div class="container area-content__inner">
      <div class="facts-box" data-animate>
        <h3>Costa Blanca Property Market — Quick Facts 2026</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Average price: €1,450/m² (range: €800–€3,500/m²)</li>
          <li>Key towns: Alicante, Torrevieja, Benidorm, Altea, Denia, Jávea</li>
          <li>Budget: €65k–€150k (apartment), €150k–€400k (villa)</li>
          <li>Airports: Alicante (ALC) — direct flights from most UK airports</li>
          <li>Rental yields: 5–8% in tourist-licence zones</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 data-animate>Costa Blanca vs Costa del Sol</h2>
      <p>The Costa Blanca (Alicante province) is a different proposition to the Costa del Sol — generally more affordable, with a larger permanent expat community and slightly less glamour. For buyers on a tighter budget, it offers significantly better value for money.</p>
      <p>Torrevieja in particular has seen strong UK buyer interest due to very low entry prices (studios from €65,000) and a well-established British community with English-speaking amenities.</p>

      <div class="internal-links" data-animate>
        <h3>Related Pages</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">← Homepage</a></li>
          <li><a href="/costa-del-sol/">Costa del Sol Properties</a></li>
          <li><a href="/apartments-costa-del-sol/">Apartments for Sale</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <LeadForm area="Costa Blanca" heading="Interested in Costa Blanca Property?" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-hero { background: var(--green); padding: 80px 0; }
.page-hero .eyebrow { color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.page-hero h1 { color: var(--white); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.page-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 16px; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; }
.area-content { padding: 64px 0; background: var(--white); }
.area-content__inner { max-width: 800px; }
.area-content__inner h2 { margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.area-content__inner h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 32px; }
.area-content__inner p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.8; }
.facts-box { background: var(--green-lt); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.facts-box h3 { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; }
.facts-box ul { margin-left: 20px; }
.facts-box li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.internal-links { background: var(--off-white); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
.internal-links h3 { font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.internal-links ul { margin-left: 0; list-style: none; }
.internal-links li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
.internal-links a { color: var(--green); font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
